  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong><br /> <br />     <u><strong> Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Prepare and cook high-quality meals consistently</li><li>Plan menus according to customer needs and budget</li><li>Supervise and train kitchen staff</li><li>Ensure food safety and hygiene standards are followed</li><li>Manage food stock, ordering, and storage</li><li>Control food costs and reduce waste</li><li>Maintain cleanliness of kitchen and equipment</li><li>Ensure timely food preparation and service</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></li></ul><ul><li>Proven experience as a cook / senior cook / executive cook</li><li>No formal qualification required</li><li>Strong knowledge of cooking techniques and food preparation</li><li>Ability to manage a kitchen team</li><li>Knowledge of food safety and hygiene practices</li><li>Ability to work under pressure and long hours</li><li>Good time management and leadership skills</li><li>Passion for cooking and quality food</li></ul>",
